rows.label: qev055106_MSG0001
rows.name: I last saw Sun'celeg on the residential-district elevator.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev055106_MSG0002
rows.name:
I watched him take it up on his way to the Ma-non
ship, then returned to the residential district myself.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev055106_MSG0003
rows.name:
I am afraid that is all that I know. Please ask other
residents of the city and see if you can track him down.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev055106_MSG0004
rows.name:
Sun'celeg is an extremely adept technologist,
and he stored several pieces of equipment inside
the Ma-non ship just in case of emergency.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev055106_MSG0005
rows.name:
His stealth camouflage units should allow us to enter
Oblivia safely.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev055106_MSG0006
rows.name:
Please do not concern yourself with us.
Focus instead on finding him and securing his safety.[ST:wait ]
